---
const founderData = {
  name: "Marcello Di Pierro",
  title: "Founder/Amazon Account Director",
  image: "/team/c.png",
  linkedin: "https://linkedin.com/in/marcello-di-pierro",
  experience: "10+ Anni di esperienza a gestire account Amazon Seller e Vendor. Ho costruito un business a 6 cifre su Amazon Seller nel mio periodo di vita in Cina, tra Shenzhen e Guangzhou."
};
---

<div class="mb-4 sm:mb-6 md:mb-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 sm:gap-5 md:gap-6">
  <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 h-auto md:h-[360px] px-4 sm:px-5 md:px-6 lg:px-8 py-4 sm:py-5 md:py-6 lg:py-8 bg-white rounded-[30px] sm:rounded-[35px] md:rounded-[40px] lg:rounded-[45px] shadow-card border border-zinc-900 flex-col justify-start items-start gap-2 sm:gap-2.5 inline-flex text-black">
    <div class="flex-col justify-start items-start gap-4 sm:gap-5 md:gap-6 lg:gap-6 flex w-full">
      <div class="w-full flex justify-between items-start"> 
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6">
            <div class="relative w-[80px] h-[80px] sm:w-[100px] sm:h-[100px] md:w-[120px] md:h-[120px] lg:w-[140px] lg:h-[140px] rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                <img src={founderData.image} alt={founderData.name} class="w-full h-full object-cover"/>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-col justify-end items-start">
                <div class="text-lg sm:text-lg md:text-lg lg:text-xl font-bold">{founderData.name}</div>
                <div class="text-base sm:text-base md:text-base lg:text-lg font-semibold">{founderData.title}</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <a href={founderData.linkedin} class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 sm:w-10 sm:h-10 md:w-11 md:h-11 lg:w-12 lg:h-12">
            <img src="/team/lng.svg" alt="LinkedIn" class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 md:w-9 md:h-9 lg:w-10 lg:h-10"/>
        </a>
      </div>
      <hr class="w-full border border-black"/>
      <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base lg:text-lg">{founderData.experience}</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full md:w-2/3 p-3 sm:p-4 md:p-5 lg:p-6">
    <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold mb-2 sm:mb-3 md:mb-4">Due Parole Dal Fondatore</h2>
    <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base lg:text-lg mb-3 sm:mb-4 md:mb-5 lg:mb-6 leading-relaxed">
      Gestisco la strategia e la visione a medio-lungo termine degli Account Amazon dei nostri partner. Mi interfaccio con loro per delineare le attività necessarie a ottenere i massimi risultati nel minor tempo possibile. Supervisiono il lavoro del nostro team interno di ADV, Design e Catalogo, coordinando quella che consideriamo ad oggi dopo anni di lavoro una "macchina perfetta" per la gestione dei canali Amazon Seller e Vendor.
    </p>
    <div class="flex justify-between items-end">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-bold text-[#F95C04]">10+</p>
        <p class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base font-normal mt-1">Anni Gestendo<br/>Account Amazon</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-bold text-[#F95C04]">20MLN+</p>
        <p class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base font-normal mt-1">Più di 20 Milioni di euro di<br/>Budget Amazon PPC Investiti</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-bold text-[#F95C04]">231%</p>
        <p class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base font-normal mt-1">Più Grande Crescita di<br/>Fatturato Registrata in 1 Anno</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>